OL,3,CWho are the candidates to be the first
OL,4,Cmayor of Hampshire and Solent?
OL,6,FThe main political parties have
OL,7,Fannounced the candidates they will be
OL,8,Fputting forward for the inaugural
OL,9,FHampshire and the Solent mayoral
OL,10,Felection.
OL,12,FOn 7 May 2026, voters across Hampshire
OL,13,Fand the Isle of Wight are due to go to
OL,14,Fthe polls to choose a directly-elected
OL,15,Fmayor for the first time.
OL,17,FLike metro mayors in London and
OL,18,FGreater Manchester, the first mayor of
OL,19,FHampshire and the Solent will be given
OL,20,Fpowers from Westminster over areas
OL,21,Fsuch as transport, housing and skills.
