OL,3,CWho are the candidates to be the first
OL,4,Cmayor of Hampshire and Solent?
OL,6,FThe mayoral combined authority will
OL,7,Fencompass the whole of the ceremonial
OL,8,Fcounty of Hampshire, including the
OL,9,Fcities of Portsmouth and Southampton.
OL,10,FIt will also include the Isle of Wight.
OL,12,FThe candidates announced so far are
OL,13,Flisted below, in alphabetical order.
OL,15,F"The new mayor has a lot to do! We
OL,16,Fmust invest in our communities and
OL,17,Fprotect our natural world. Public
OL,18,Fservices have been stripped back to
OL,19,Fbreaking point by successive
OL,20,Fgovernments, to the point that many
OL,21,Fare looking for a new alternative."
