OL,3,CWho are the candidates to be the first
OL,4,Cmayor of Hampshire and Solent?
OL,6,FCllr Fielker is a Southampton city
OL,7,Fcouncillor and was leader of the
OL,8,Fauthority from January 2024 until July
OL,9,F2025. She has lived in the area for 11
OL,10,Fyears, according to the Labour Party.
OL,12,F"After years of underinvestment from
OL,13,Fcentral government, this is a once in
OL,14,Fa generation opportunity to bring
OL,15,Fproper leadership and accountability
OL,16,Fto our area, securing the resources we
OL,17,Fneed to deliver real improvements to
OL,18,Fthe place we all call home."
