OL,6,FMs Jones has been the area's police
OL,7,Fand crime commissioner (PCC) since
OL,8,F2021. She was previously a Portsmouth
OL,9,Fcity councillor and was leader of the
OL,10,Fcouncil from 2014 to 2018.
OL,12,F"I'm not a career politician. I served
OL,13,Fin the Royal Navy for over 30 years
